### ============================================================
### MANAGEMENT / SERVICES
### ============================================================

### List Services
GET {{base_api_url}}/management/services
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Get Service
GET {{base_api_url}}/management/services/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

### Create Service
POST {{base_api_url}}/management/services
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Premium Package",
  "limit": 20,
  "description": "20 lessons per month with materials",
  "price": 299.99
}

### Update Service
PUT {{base_api_url}}/management/services/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Basic Service - Updated",
  "price": 109.99
}

### Delete Service
DELETE {{base_api_url}}/management/services/1
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
